Pages.Text: In the very early years after the Olthoi were overthrown, the land was constantly under attack from Tumeroks.  Hence, a man named Witshire built a fort upon the ruins of an Empyrean fortress, out to the west of Cragstone.  Fort Witshire stood tall and proud for but a short time, for the tumeroks were driven back, and it was soon abandoned.  Now it stands alone, out to the west of Cragstone in the fields.
